<div name="prices_active_element_original">
<div class="inline" id="goods_price_block_14438792"></div>
<script>
var pricerawjson = '%7B%22price%22%3A4999%2C%22status%22%3A%22active%22%2C%22sell_status%22%3A%22unavailable%22%2C%22pl_bonus_charge_pcs%22%3A%220%22%2C%22pl_use_instant_bonus%22%3A%220%22%2C%22old_price%22%3A0%2C%22old_usd_price%22%3A0%2C%22price_formatted%22%3A%224%20999%22%2C%22old_price_formatted%22%3A%220%22%2C%22usd_price%22%3A189.72%2C%22is_price_deviated%22%3A%220%22%2C%22atp%22%3Afalse%7D';
var price_json = App.getService('JSON').parse(decodeURIComponent(pricerawjson));
price_json.icon_view = 'tile';
price_json.price_unit = 'грн';
price_json.price_old_unit = 'грн';
price_json.hide_old_price = 0;
price_json.show_usd_price = false;
var priceFormatter = new GoodsPriceBlockFormatter_class(price_json);
